author: Guerrilla Miniature Games
description:
What's up gang it's the MONDAY SHOW... monthly free episode. This is our hang out where we talk about the week that was and the week to come while we get ourselves in order for the many hobby tasks ahead. Hang out, listen and ask questions in the chat and get in on the PATRON MAILBAG Q&A we do every week on GMG. 

Let's go!!!
title: The MONDAY SHOW - Monthly FREE-PISODE - Let's talk upcoming games and news of the week.
